# BE conventions

## Layers (khong dao nguoc phu thuoc)

- `Domain` — entities, enums; khong EF, khong HTTP.
- `Application` — DTOs, interfaces, services (Dijkstra, use cases).
- `Infrastructure` — EF `AppDbContext`, MQTT, JWT, HTTP clients.
- `API` — controllers, hubs, middleware, `Program.cs`.

## DB / n8n compatibility (bat buoc)

| C# | SQL |
|----|-----|
| `Member` | `Members` — `MemberName` computed, khong ghi EF |
| `RobotLog` | `Robot_Logs` — giu `battery`, `location`, `status`, `timestamp` |
| Views keyless | `PurchaseHistory`, `Store_Map`, `Blocked_Aisles`, `Real_Time_Stock` |

## API

- REST + Swagger; SignalR hub `/hubs/robot`; MQTT topic `smartmarketbot/robot/{code}/...`
- Port dev: **5000**; connection string trong `appsettings.Development.json`
- Async/await; global exception middleware — khong nuot loi im lang

## Tranh

- Them package / refactor lon ngoai task
- Doi ten cot bang AI/n8n dang dung
- Commit secret (JWT key, SA password) vao git
